<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Login Alert - XroboFly</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .header {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B35 0%, #F7931E 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .alert-icon {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0 20px;
        }
        .alert-icon span {
            font-size: 64px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 40px 40px;
        }
        .greeting {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .greeting p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .login-details {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .login-details h3 {
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .detail-label span {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: right;
            max-width: 60%;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .location-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .location-info h4 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .location-item {
            display: flex;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
        .location-item strong {
            min-width: 120px;
            color: #667eea;
        }
        .location-item span {
            color: #666;
        }
        .security-warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .security-warning h4 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .security-warning p {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .action-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .action-button a {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dc3545;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .secure-note {
            background: #d4edda;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .secure-note p {
            color: #155724;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .footer p {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #111827;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üöÅ</div>
            <h1>Security Alert</h1>
            <p>New Login Detected</p>
        </div>

        <div class="alert-icon">
            <span>üîî</span>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                <h2>Hello, {{name}}!</h2>
                <p>We detected a new login to your XroboFly account. If this was you, great! If not, please take immediate action.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="login-details">
                <h3>üìä Login Information</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">
                        <span>üìÖ</span> Date & Time:
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{loginTime}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">
                        <span>üåê</span> IP Address:
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ipAddress}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">
                        <span>üíª</span> Device:
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{deviceInfo}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">
                        <span>üìç</span> Location:
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{location}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="location-info">
                <h4>üó∫Ô∏è Additional Details</h4>
                <div class="location-item">
                    <strong>Browser:</strong>
                    <span>{{browser}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="location-item">
                    <strong>Operating System:</strong>
                    <span>{{os}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="location-item">
                    <strong>Email:</strong>
                    <span>{{email}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="secure-note">
                <p><strong>‚úÖ Was this you?</strong> No action needed. You can safely ignore this email.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="security-warning">
                <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Didn't recognize this login?</h4>
                <p>If you didn't authorize this login, your account may be compromised. Please secure your account immediately by changing your password and reviewing your recent activity.</p>
                <div class="action-button">
                    <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/reset-password">Secure My Account Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="secure-note">
                <p><strong>üîí Security Tip:</strong> Always use strong, unique passwords and enable two-factor authentication when available.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated security notification from XroboFly.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:security@ecom.com">security@ecom.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">¬© {{year}} XroboFly. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
